ged to use the values provided via sdf. </p>\n<p>This is important for easier testing of hose mating as we don't want to have to pick up the hose every time just to test mating.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-05-06T18:30:21.308747+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-05-07T21:29:40.404537+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 248}